bio:
Gilfre is an Imperial lumberjack residing at the Mixwater Mill in Eastmarch hold, which she also owns and operates.
Gilfre once had several workers at the mill, but they left her to fight in the Civil War. She has since been having trouble running the mill by herself.
Gilfre sells sawn logs at a price of 200 gold per 20 logs.
If the Dragonborn has a high reputation with Gilfre, she will allow them to cut her logs at the sawmill for free.
name: Gilfre
